            Profiles of Our Work
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            World-Class Faculty
                    

                Change is swift. How can researchers recalibrate their ethical stances?
            









                            Dynamic Student Body
                    

                What use are cheap glasses when people can't get their eyes checked?
            









                            Inclusive Excellence in STEM
                    

                UIC educators are redesigning STEM courses to foster excellence in inclusion.
            









                            Building Math Educator Capacity
                    

                LSRI staff are providing useful resources to enhance teachers’ capacity to teach PreK–6 mathematics.
            









                            Reforming Education Through Scholarship
                    

                Current students are arriving at solutions to teaching and learning issues of today.
            









                            Ethical Obligations of Our Alumni
                    

                Our alumni apply their knowledge to affect change.
            












